ost story as a literary form. In her concluding chapter, the author also traces the influence of ancient ghost stories on modern ghost story writers, a topic that will interest all readers and scholars of tales of hauntings.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aClassical literaturexHistory and criticism. 0aGhost stories, ClassicalxHistory and criticism. 0aGhosts in literature. 0aGhostszGreece. 0aGhostszRome. 0aLiterature and folklorezGreece. 0aLiterature and folklorezRome. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.7560/72507240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780292757325423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780292757325/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LT  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK